[codex] - **Multi-cell design (Study 5 form):** report balance per condition cell, e.g., `Initial six-person panels were 60.7% women in the women overrepresented condition, with balance across feedback conditions (59.8% vs. 61.6%; t(...) = ..., p = ..., 95% CI = [...])`. Repeat for the other condition.
